#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.230:0.2"
msgid "23. Duccaritavagga "
msgstr "23. Bad Conduct "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.230:0.3"
msgid "230. Duppaññasutta "
msgstr "230. Witless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.230, sc1
msgctxt "an4.230:1.1"
msgid "… pe … Assaddho hoti, dussīlo hoti, kusīto hoti, duppañño hoti … pe … saddho hoti, sīlavā hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti—"
msgstr "“A foolish person … makes much bad karma. … They’re faithless, unethical, lazy, and witless. … An astute person … makes much merit. … They’re faithful, ethical, energetic, and wise. "

msgctxt "an4.230:1.2"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti. "
msgstr "When an astute, competent good person has these four qualities they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.230:1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

